\mathbb{R}^3
\to
\mathbb{R}^3
h:\Bbb R^3\to\Bbb R^3\;\;,\;\;h(1,1,1)=(2,2,0)\;,\;h(1,2,1)=(3,3,0)\;,\;h(1,0,0)=(1,0,1)
\;\Bbb B:=\{(1,1,1)\,,\,(1,2,1)\,,\,(1,0,0)\}\;
\;\Bbb R^3\;
\;v\in\Bbb R^3\;
v=a(1,1,1)+b(1,2,1)+c(1,0,0)\;,\;\;a,b,c\in\Bbb R
h(v)=ah(1,1,1)+bh(1,2,1)+ch(1,0,0)=a(2,2,0)+b(3,3,0)+c(1,0,1)
